Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: pixelpop
Version: 0.1
Summary: Meant for use with numpyro and jax, package for fitting the GW population with a nonparameteric binning scheme, where bins are correlated with only their nearest neighbors. Meant for inferring the GW population distribution nonparameterically in higher dimensions.
